  "146": "D-037 — Gmail OAuth via a plain refresh-token POST (no `oauth2` crate); `base64` promoted from transitive to direct dependency",
  "147": "model_swap.rs",
  "148": "D-040 — Pending (pre-approval) `ActionRequest`s are persisted in a new `action_requests` table",
  "149": "D-041 — `email.create_draft`'s digest composition: payload = `{subject, body}`, target = `{thread_id, connector, account_role, recipients}`",
  "150": "D-043 — `lyra.ui.preview` is extended (not duplicated) to propose the exact reviewed draft and attach the approval button",
  "151": "D-044 — Approved draft creation dispatches kernel-side; no new shell spawn",
  "152": "D-045 — WYSIWYS: a truncated preview refuses an approval button rather than splitting the message",
  "153": "D-046 — Grant budgets are enforced kernel-dispatch-side; the artifact budget counts only shell-initiated puts",
  "154": "D-047 — Task tokens are hashed at rest; expired grants are swept",
  "155": "D-048 — `artifact.activate` is the single canonical activation action id; every runtime proposal requires uniform owner approval; prompt templates are excluded from proposable kinds",
  "156": "D-049 — Capability specs are backfilled for subsystems implemented inside earlier slices",
  "157": "D-050 — `max_model_calls` is enforced with an atomic upsert, not a count-then-compare",
  "158": "D-006 — Identity is not authority",
  "159": "D-011 — Approval must be digest-bound",
  "160": "D-012 — Audit stores private payloads by encrypted/hash reference",
  "161": "D-013 — Dynamic behavior easy; dynamic authority hard",
  "162": "D-014 — Bootstrap/setup secrets bypass shell/model context",
  "163": "D-015 — Phase 1 should avoid final email send",
  "164": "D-016 — Capability packs are candidate profiles, not live authority",
  "165": "D-017 — Personas grant no authority",
  "166": "D-018 — Routes are declarative artifacts, not kernel code",
  "167": "D-020 — Railway/Docker/VPS are deployment targets, not core architecture",
  "168": "D-025 — Rust/Tokio substrate: storage, audit chain, and secrets handling",
  "169": "D-027 — Multi-provider model gateway with per-provider auth mode",
  "170": "D-028 — Canonical artifact format is YAML+serde; digests are `sha256:` over canonical JSON",
  "171": "D-029 — Gmail OAuth scopes: `readonly` + `compose`, send hard-denied at the gate",
